high_descs: Turn right towards the counter with the toaster on top.
Pick up the gray knife on the right of the toaster.
Turn around and go to the white round table in the left corner.
Cut the apple behind the white cup into three parts.
Turn around and go to the front of refrigerator on the left across the kitchen
Place the knife inside the refrigerator on the middle shelf.
Turn right and go back to the white table in the right corner.
Take one piece of the apple from the table.
Turn around and go to the microwave above the stove.
Remove the apple after heating it in the microwave.
Turn left and go to the front of the refrigerator.
Place the apple piece on the middle shelf in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated piece of apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter.
Go to the round table.
Slice the apple on the table near the center.
Turn and take the butter knife to the fridge.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Go back to the round table.
Pick up an apple slice on the table.
Go to the microwave.
Heat the apple slice in the microwave.
Turn and go to the fridge.
Put the hot apple slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot apple slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Take a right and then right again and walk over to the white table.
Cut the apple in thirds with the knife.
Turn right and over to the counter, take a right for one step, take a left and walk to the far counter, then right to face the refrigerator.
Open the fridge, put the knife in it, and then close the door.
Turn right and walk over to the wall, turn right and over to the white table.
Pick up the piece of apple closest to the grey cup.
Turn around for one step, take a left and follow the counter until you are in front of the stove and stop.
Open the microwave, put the apple in with the peel facing out, and shut the door, turn on the microwave for a few second, then remove the apple and shut the door again.
Turn around for two steps, turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the apple on center front of the top shelf and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and a cooked apple in the refrigerator.
